Dependencies:
g++
openmp
libnoise (libraries and headers)
python2.7
python2.7-tk
python-imaging-tk

To install dependencies on Ubuntu 11.04:
sudo apt-get install libnoise-dev python2.7-tk python-imaging-tk -y

To checkout from git:
git clone git://github.com/sbobovyc/DCS.git

To compile:
cd DCS/DCS
make

To run gui:
bash run-DCS-app.sh

To change libnoise include path:
cd DCS
open the Makefile
change LIBNOISEINC to libnoise include path
